{"tid":2019023,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高官局長子女在內地讀書，只會有利，係唔會有任何嘅弊","createTime":"2020-05-16T04:02:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T04:46:42.000Z","uid":272805,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"680446b96524cd74b947b437ffb82a18073aae5d","tid":2019023,"uid":272805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T04:02:22.000Z","msg":"如果係外國讀書，其實有很強的倒流效應，<br />\n下一屆局長既仔女學生，他們會參考、他們會學習，<br />\n外國老師會教導佢地<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">咩係民主自由，投票權利</span></span>，所以影響不能輕視。<br />\n係祖國讀書就唔同，話哂要五千年中華文化，外國教學點比得上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n教育局官員係咪應該要以身所則呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n擁抱中華文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，拋棄外國勢力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我要真批鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa6fdb271e62f1af3ad80c39c660538d778849a9","tid":2019023,"uid":59737,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T04:02:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b234e6fc4d1399ba185e441ed3706413c447d39","tid":2019023,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T04:03:56.000Z","msg":"中國人嘅夢想（aka 中國夢）就係移民，離開中國。亦都即係愛國。"},{"pid":"5c5d7d8a503e8d70c4bfd77e8e9a85b7ecfae77f","tid":2019023,"uid":272805,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6b234e6fc4d1399ba185e441ed3706413c447d39","tid":2019023,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T04:03:56.000Z","msg":"中國人嘅夢想（aka 中國夢）就係移民，離開中國。亦都即係愛國。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T04:06:00.000Z","msg":"唔入中國，又點離開中國呢<br />\n第一步都未做，應該要做左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e4e988c2e1294065af25fc05c287d59272bb35a","tid":20